data.description: Differentiable manifolds, vector bundles, implicit function theorem, submersions and immersions, vector fields and flows, foliations and Frobenius theorem, differential forms and exterior calculus, integration and Stokes' theorem, De Rham theory, Riemannian metrics. Familiarity with basic undergraduate analysis coursesMATH 521and522orMATH 621) is strongly recommended.
data.title: DIFFERENTIABLE MANIFOLDS
